{"tid":1989853,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[武肺] 環保署：空氣污染水平持續上升或達至嚴重水平","createTime":"2020-04-26T09:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T17:37:58.000Z","uid":176553,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c0395192a799c86fc543fec7854a8483b082ff39","tid":1989853,"uid":176553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:43:43.000Z","msg":"環保署表示，空氣污染水平持續上升，預測空氣質素健康指數可能達至嚴重水平。<br />\n<br />\n環保署指，受一股大陸氣流影響，本港今日天氣乾燥，部分時間有陽光，吹輕微至和緩東北風，早上起錄得的臭氧及粒子水平都較正常高。<br />\n<br />\n受背景污染較高的氣團影響，日間的陽光有利光化煙霧現象，令臭氧及微細懸浮粒子在珠江三角洲區域內迅速形成，現時多區包括荃灣、屯門及大埔等，空氣質素健康指數已達9，而東涌更至10。<br />\n<br />\n環保署呼籲，當健康風險級別達到甚高或嚴重水平時，一般市民應減少在戶外逗留及體力消耗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b990efe58b4a9ffa28e5a0c5d6e8193915b20a","tid":1989853,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:44:16.000Z","msg":"開工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4753ca87f14d56cf0c4d50bde603d39516814d7b","tid":1989853,"uid":284855,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"大陸復工的指標"},{"pid":"f09fbce605784ba8f0e43445c9d5b3c48294f800","tid":1989853,"uid":126508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4753ca87f14d56cf0c4d50bde603d39516814d7b","tid":1989853,"uid":284855,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"大陸復工的指標"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"火粥指數嚟"},{"pid":"e3108a3f777e463843fb931b6434484e620571ed","tid":1989853,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:58:36.000Z","msg":"// 受一股大陸氣流影響 //<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"